tg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/Tr%C3%B9ng-qu%C3%A1-Hoan-%C3%81i-gi%C3%A1p-c%E1%BA%A3nh-L%C3%A3nh-Kh%C3%AA-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-bhm4GvCW0tNVKO-vl7koUg">Trùng quá Hoan Ái giáp cảnh Lãnh Khê kiều - 重過驩愛夾境冷溪橋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Gia-Kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-8LnLdnpSw5BT75bj7y3sNQ">Trương Gia Khẩu - 張家口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-8k5-bGU03Z_txBNZHdLGbQ">Liên Hoành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A3o-H%E1%BA%A3o-thi/poem-ZLgiAlRmZdlWf7MkDKd1sg">Trương Hảo Hảo thi - 張好好詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-T%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3/Xu%C3%A2n-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-sJ-9e7ScGRZCvV9naTqqIQ">Xuân sự - 春事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-T%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3/author-vKbY4mxW66T2uFN2-wgrVw">Hồng Tư Quỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
